Titolo: Metro Exodus

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Metro Exodus is a first-person shooter video game developed by 4A Games and published by Deep Silver. It is the third installment in the Metro video game trilogy based on Dmitry Glukhovsky's novels, following the events of Metro 2033 and Metro: Last Light. It released in 2019 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, Xbox One and Stadia and in 2020 for Amazon Luna. A Linux and macOS conversion was released in 2021. An enhanced version of the game released for Microsoft Windows on May 6, 2021 and was later released for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S on June 18, 2021. The game received positive reviews from critics.